RESPONSE - Encourage It:
"Smart. You should. Most investors will run similar cash numbers. Where we're different is we specialize in foreclosure situations specifically — so we can do loan takeovers if that works better, and we understand the timeline pressure you're under."

COMPETITIVE POSITIONING:
